  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_20",
    "english": "Taimanin, mainly on spying or assassination missions. She is usually on a mission about people who are related to the demon realm, not the demons directly. Since she takes this kind of special missions a lot, she ostensibly works as a broker who connects humans and demons, but searches for evil hiding in the dark as a Taimanin. A talented one who can toy with men with her words, even during battle.",
